story: MIT African Students' Association - ASA updated their profile picture.
message: It's true people! MIT and Wellesley ASA have decided to partner up for our annual Cultural Show. If you care at all for delectable food, dynamic music and the priceless company of your own, you really do not want to miss out on this event. Come through y'all! XD

story: MIT African Students' Association - ASA updated their cover photo.
message:
Shout out to the new MIT ASA Executive Committee.
Thanks so much to the outgoing committee for making last year enjoyable.

New ASA Exec:
President: Pelkins Ajanoh
Vice President: Emmanuel Azuh Mensah
Secretary: Lisa Nyasha Madungwe
Treasurer: Jessica Quaye
Academic Chair: Kudzaishe George Zharare
Professional Chair: Nitah Kelsy Onsongo
Sports Chair: Lesian Elias
WebMaster: Audace Nakeshimana
Social Co Chair: Raveen Nzilani
Social Co Chair: Simi Bright
Public Relations Chair: Samira Okudo

comments.message: Congalations Jessica, Nitah and Raveen. All the best in your new roles.
